                   SAMPLE SHAREWARE CATALOG LISTING

ImagiSOFT's  extraordinary  game of Chinese Checkers for  1-6  players
features  animated  graphics and brings you all the challenge  of  the
traditional board game.  As in the board game, to win you must be  the
first  player  to move all your marbles to the opposite  side  of  the
board.  The 6 players (represented by animated icons, a Dragon,  Wind,
Flower, Mantis, Tiger, and Peacock) can be played either by people  or
by the computer. It uses the keyboard or MS-compatible mouse, requires
EGA or VGA,  and  640K of memory.   Nominated for Best New Product and
Best Entertainment Software  at  the Summer Shareware Seminar in 1992.
Run Chinese Checkers from your floppy by entering the command CHINESE,
but it will run faster if you install it to your hard drive  with  the
command A:INSTALL.


                    DISTRIBUTING CHINESE CHECKERS

Anyone distributing Chinese Checkers for any kind of remuneration must
first contact ImagiSOFT, Inc. at the address below for  authorization.
This authorization is automatically granted to distributors recognized
by the Association of Shareware Professionals (ASP) as adhering to its
guidelines for shareware distributors, and such distributors may begin
offering  Chinese Checkers immediately; however, ImagiSOFT, Inc.  must
still  be advised so that the distributor can be kept up-to-date  with
the latest version of Chinese Checkers.

If you are going to distribute Chinese Checkers in a compressed  file,
please  use  the  name CC13.??? (.ZIP, .ARC,  .LZH,  etc).   We  would
appreciate  if  you would distribute our  original  CC12.ZIP  whenever
possible so that new users can be assured that they aren't receiving a
program infected with a virus.

Please include the following files in your distribution copy:

    CHINESE.EXE   main program
    CHINESE.TXT   registration info, license agreement, etc.
    CC_ORDER.TXT  order form
    CHINESE.WL    graphics file
    REGISTER.WL      "      "
    CC_I_1.WL        "      "
    CC_I_2.WL        "      "
    CC_I_3.WL        "      "
    CC_I_4.WL        "      "
    CC_I_5.WL        "      "
    CC_I_6.WL        "      "
    INSTALL.EXE   install to Hard Drive
    INSTALL.FIL   install script file
    CHINESE.BAT   run from Hard Drive
    READ.ME       brief description, how to install, etc.

IMPORTANT  NOTE:  The Chinese Checkers program checks for  missing  or
altered  files.  If either of our *.TXT files has been altered  or  if
one of the *.WL files is missing, the program will exit to DOS.

